long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🕶️ History AutoDelete - Tabbee's Story 🎉

History AutoDelete - Tabbee plugin was born as a solution for everyone who feels the need to protect your privacy. Completely eliminating the hassle of manually clearing browser history, cookies 🍪 and cache 🗑️, this plugin was developed to protect users' privacy and improve browser performance.

Many users used to complain about the difficulty of clearing browser history on a regular basis. Therefore, History AutoDelete - Tabbee aimed to automate tools such as privacy protection and browser history cleaner, allowing everyone to use a safer and faster browser. 🚀

Now, let's explain in detail how to install this plugin and how to use it!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🌟 Why History AutoDelete - Tabbee?

✔️ Protect Your Privacy

     🔸History AutoDelete - Tabbee helps you protect your privacy by automatically clearing your browser history, cookies and cache. 🔒

✔️ Improve Browser Performance

    🔸You can improve your browser's performance by eliminating unnecessary data. This extension acts as Chrome data cleaner and internet history remover. ⚡

✔️ Easy to Use

    🔸The plugin is very easy to use thanks to its simple and user-friendly interface. It offers all the cleaning tools you need in one place, without unnecessary complexity. 🛠️


History AutoDelete - Tabbee is a history wipe extension solution to keep your browser clean and secure. With its advanced privacy protection tools and easy-to-use interface, you can keep your browser data under control and have a safer internet experience.

🔗 Download Now and Protect Your Privacy! 😊


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

📥 History AutoDelete - How to Install Tabbee? 🔧 (General Information)

✔️Open the Chrome Web Store

     🔸Go to the Chrome Web Store page in your browser. Type “History AutoDelete - Tabbee” in the search box to find the extension. 🔍

✔️Install Plugin

     🔸After opening the History AutoDelete - Tabbee plugin page, click the “Add to Chrome” button in the upper right corner. After that, the extension will be added to your browser. This extension automates features like auto history wipe and cookie cleaner.

✔️Installation Completed

     🔸After the installation is complete, you will see the History AutoDelete - Tabbee icon in the upper right corner of your browser. You can adjust the settings of the plugin via this icon. ⚙️

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

⚙️ How to Use the Plugin? 🖱️

✔️Open Plugin

     🔸You can open History AutoDelete - Tabbee by clicking on the plugin icon in the upper right corner of your browser. The plugin interface is very simple and user-friendly. 👨‍💻

✔️Determine the Time Interval ⏱️

     🔸The Time Range Selection section allows you to choose when you want to clear your browser history. For example, you can set a cleaning time in the last hour, last 24 hours, last week or custom time range. This feature allows you to automatically manage browser data with auto history wipe.

✔️Select Items to Clean 🗃️

    🔸In the Items to Clean section you can select the data you want to clean. In this section, there are different options such as browser history, cookies, cache, downloads and form data. Everything you select will be automatically cleaned by the plugin. You can make your browser faster with cache cleaner and cookie cleaner features. 💨

✔️Start the Cleanup Process

    🔸By clicking the “Clean Now” button on the plugin, you can immediately start cleaning the selected items. 🔄
